{
  "stem": "14724.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 25.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And her name was Toni.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was just like looking into a mirror.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I went-- they took me home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She made a cup of tea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said to me, have you been in touch with your Uncle David?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, well, who's Uncle David?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Your father's eldest brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, where is he?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, in Miami, she said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, what about Erika?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, Erika's the aunt who's-- who's clothes I used to have to wear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she too, was in Miami.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So Toni picks up the telephone-- Are these some of the relatives that went to South America?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my father's family--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--who went to New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we really didn't have anything to do with them, for a very simple explanation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had come to America about 1936, '37.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father had pleaded with my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they came with money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had pleaded with her to send him enough to bring us out, and he would work until he paid it back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she replied-- and I remember that letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She replied, not saying I can't, but saying, I won't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he never forgave her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As far as I was concerned, I had no family on my father's side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, Toni picked up the telephone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she knew me as Ellen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she's talking to Uncle David about Ellen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He doesn't know who Ellen is, because I'm Kerry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, try Kerry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had a feeling the phone was going to explode.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this man is in his 80's.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it had happened Erika was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the only thing I could here was my Uncle David, whose name actually is Fritz, saying, when are you coming?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So once I decided that, you know, there's no way.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
